                <p class="text-gray-300">We begin with a deep-dive analysis of your current local search footprint, identifying strengths, weaknesses, and competitive gaps across your Google Business Profile, citations, and on-page elements.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-black font-bold text-sm">2</span></div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-2">Google Business Profile Optimization</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300">Your Google Business Profile (GBP) is your most critical local ranking factor. We perform a complete optimization of your profile, ensuring every section is complete, accurate, and aligned with best practices.</p>
