                <p class="text-gray-300">We identify high-value local search terms and "near me" queries that your target customers are using, forming the foundation of your content and on-page optimization strategy.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-black font-bold text-sm">4</span></div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-2">Citation Building & Management</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300">Consistency is key. We build and manage your business citations across dozens of relevant local directories, ensuring your Name, Address, and Phone (NAP) information is accurate everywhere.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-black font-bold text-sm">5</span></div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-2">On-Page Local Optimization</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300">We implement local schema markup, create dedicated location pages for multi-location businesses, and optimize your website's content to be geographically relevant and authoritative.</p>
