                <p class="text-gray-300">We help you monitor and respond to customer reviews across platforms, building social proof and trust, which are significant factors in local search rankings.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-black font-bold text-sm">7</span></div>
