            <div>
                <h4 class="font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-2">Performance Tracking</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300">We continuously monitor your local rankings, organic traffic, and conversion metrics, providing transparent reports that demonstrate the direct impact of our efforts on your business goals.</p>
            </div>
