    <h2 class="text-2xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-6">Best Practices and Tools</h2>
    <p class="text-white mb-6">
      Effective local SEO requires a focus on key areas that search engines use to determine local ranking. This includes maintaining consistent business information, managing your online reputation, and leveraging the right tools to monitor performance.
    </p>

