        </svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="px-6 pb-6">
        <p class="text-white">Pricing varies based on the scope and competitiveness of your market. Monthly retainers for small businesses typically range from $300 to $2,000. More competitive markets or enterprise-level campaigns can range from $2,500 to $5,000+ per month.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="group bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-xl mb-4">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-orbitron font-bold text-primary">How long does it take to see results from local SEO?</h3>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
        </svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="px-6 pb-6">
        <p class="text-white">While some improvements can be seen within the first few weeks (like from Google Business Profile optimization), significant results in local rankings and traffic typically take 3 to 6 months. Local SEO is a long-term strategy that builds sustainable visibility.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="group bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-xl mb-4">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-orbitron font-bold text-primary">What's the difference between local SEO and regular SEO?</h3>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
        </svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="px-6 pb-6">
        <p class="text-white">Regular (or national) SEO focuses on ranking for broad keywords across the country or globe. Local SEO adds a geographical component, focusing on ranking for keywords within a specific service area. It involves location-specific strategies like citation management and Google Business Profile optimization that are not central to regular SEO.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <div class="bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 p-8 rounded-xl text-center my-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-4">Get Your Free Local SEO Analysis</h3>
        <p class="text-white max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6">Dominate local search results and drive more customers to your business with proven local SEO strategies. Let us analyze your current standing and provide a roadmap for success.</p>
        <a href="/#contact" class="bg-primary text-black font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/80 transition-colors">
            Get Local SEO Analysis
